enhanced_by.reason: The futuresAccountV2 method requires the sub-account to have futures enabled, which is done by the enableFutures method.
The futuresAccountV2 method may require assets to be transferred to the futures account, which is done by the futuresTransfer method.
Both futuresAccountV2 and futuresAccountSummaryV2 methods provide information about the sub-account's futures account, making them suitable for constructing assertions.
The futuresPositionRiskV2 method provides position risk information, which can be used to verify the state of the futures account after invoking futuresAccountV2.
